data.title: 3D & 2D CAD Models
data.meta_description: 3D CAD models user library for 3D previewing, 3D printing and 3D webgl sharing. PARTcommunity is a library for 2D & 3D CAD models of supplier and standard parts.
data.text:
PARTcloud.net APP

Upload your 3D CAD models for free on PARTcloud.net and show them to your friends and co-workers with the PARTcloud.net app.

The App's Features:

Sketch search for finding any part easily

Mixed reality with your 3D part

See your 3D part as anaglyph red/cyan model
